      "created": "2022-03-29T16:54:04.152+0000",
      "description": "We can control the maximum resources an application can use by adjusting the resource limit threshold of queues.\r\n\r\nIt resolves the problem applications starve when a single application takes all resources of the queue.\r\n\r\nIt can be quite effective when all tasks of a queue need to be treated fairly.",
